    public class SpatialIndividualDescriptor
extends it.emarolab.owloop.aMORDescriptor.utility.MORIndividualBase
implements it.emarolab.owloop.aMORDescriptor.MORIndividual.Disjoint<SpatialIndividualDescriptor>, it.emarolab.owloop.aMORDescriptor.MORIndividual.Type<SpatialClassDescriptor>, it.emarolab.owloop.aMORDescriptor.MORIndividual.DataLink<it.emarolab.owloop.aMORDescriptor.utility.dataProperty.MORHierarchicalDataProperty>, it.emarolab.owloop.aMORDescriptor.MORIndividual.ObjectLink<SpatialObjectPropertyDescriptor>
    The OWLOOP Descriptor for an individual representing a concrete Object.

    This is an OWLNamedIndividual Descriptor based on the OWLOOP API. It is in charge to synchronise the types of this individual, its data and object properties as well as disjoint individuals.

    File: it.emarolab.sit.owloopDescriptor.SpatialIndividualDescriptor
